N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4624.4 - Notification when no games are played

State Regulations

When no games are held on any date when a license
authorizes them to be held, a notification to that effect must be filed with
the clerk or department, the officer and the commission. Notes
